One of my favorites. Here's my changes Mama Mia: Use thick cut bacon instead of pancetta (if hard to find). Also added a bit of the bacon runoff (2tsp) with the olive oil. Now that's heart smart. 2x the thyme, 8 cups water, 30 oz beans, 6-7 oz spinach, and skip the green beans. FOR THE PISTOU: 2 cups basil, 1/2-1 cup parmesan. Lastly, DO NOT go without the pistou or reggiano rinds or you'll miss the boat. Ciao.

